data.description:
This 6-acre property is located just 10 minutes from town but feels like country living. It has a fenced backyard, workshop, 2 storage buildings, detached covered parking, and attached garage. The house is a brick home with a metal roof and fireplace. It needs some work, but it is ready to live in as is.

This property is perfect for someone who wants to start a small ranch or homestead. There is plenty of room to roam and the mature trees provide shade and privacy. The covered porch is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the outdoors. If you are looking for a property with plenty of space to relax and enjoy the outdoors, this is the perfect place for you. Schedule a tour today!
